{
  "id": "kor-phaeron",
  "name": "Kor Phaeron",
  "titles": "Kor Phaeron First Captain of the Word Bearers, Master of Faith, Priest-king of Colchis",
  "lore": "Scorned by many in his Legion as a ‘half Astartes’, Kor Phaeron was Lorgar’s surrogate father and his tutor in the ancient ways and rites of Colchis. By the time the XVIIth Legion was united with its Primarch, Kor Phaeron was too old to undergo the full implantation process, but so favoured was he in the eyes of his Primarch that he received the most potent of augments possible to bestow upon a man short of elevation to the Legiones Astartes, and was declared First Captain. In this role, Kor Phaeron exerted great influence upon his Primarch and within his Legion, his conviction and zeal unfettered and undiminished.",
